97
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,360
Jingzhi,

98
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,320
if possible,

99
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,360
I hope your life in the future

100
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,920
will always be joyful

101
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,040
without any bitterness.

102
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,880
Mr. Fang,

103
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,320
I admit

104
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,000
my inner dependence on you.

105
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,800
But this also leaves me at a loss.

106
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,600
Because I feel

107
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,640
that, with my background,

108
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,760
I might not be

109
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,160
in the same world as you.

110
00:05:37,504 --> 00:05:38,624
♪Despite the burning longing♪

111
00:05:38,624 --> 00:05:40,320
♪The grandeur hasn't faded♪

112
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,640
I don't care.

113
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,320
I only remember

114
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,960
my heartbeat when I first saw you.

115
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,280
I remember the umbrella

116
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,840
you handed to me on a cold, rainy night

117
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,440
and how you waited anxiously

118
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,000
at the train station,

119
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,720
as well as the dish that gave me

120
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,680
the feeling of home.

121
00:06:02,387 --> 00:06:06,803
♪Let our tale unfold♪

122
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,000
Look.

123
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,320
Slow down.

124
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,280
Don't run around.

125
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,280
Slow down.

126
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,600
Stop.

127
00:07:19,891 --> 00:07:21,696
(Xuntang Fireworks Factory)

128
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,200
Many are injured.

129
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:25,880
Exactly.

130
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,760
Make way, please.

131
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,000
Make way.

132
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,560
What a mishap!

133
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,320
This town's been safe for centuries.

134
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:33,480
This explosion is driving me mad.

135
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,960
Have you found its cause?

136
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,000
An hour ago,

137
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,680
which was just after midnight,

138
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,360
a car was passing by the factory

139
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,240
and exploded.

140
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,400
The car lost control,

141
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,240
ran into the factory,

142
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:46,400
and ignited the explosives inside,
causing a chain of explosions.

143
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,480
Do you all hear?

144
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,800
I can't believe this.

145
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,880
How could there be a bomb in the car?

146
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,560
Chief,

147
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,160
(Chief Hu Lai)
I don't know.

148
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:57,160
How was the bomb in the car detonated?

149
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:58,560
Well,

150
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,800
I don't know either.

151
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,960
That's really coincidental.

152
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,040
Why did the bomb have to clash
with the explosives?

153
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:07,240
I still don't know.

154
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,960
You know nothing
at such a critical moment.

155
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,400
What can I expect from you?

156
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,480
Who arrived at the scene first?

157
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:14,680
Chief Hu,

158
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,560
I was patrolling nearby at the time.

159
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:17,760
I heard the noise

160
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,160
and rushed over immediately.

161
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,360
Did you see anyone

162
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,760
suspicious at the scene?

163
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,680
No.

164
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,360
To be precise,

165
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,280
it was already a mess when I arrived.

166
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,160
Did you see them or not?

167
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,440
Chief,

168
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:30,760
I am not sure.

169
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:33,560
Someone is coming out.

170
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,200
That's so pitiful.

171
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,160
What are you doing?

172
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,960
Can't you see they are busy?

173
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,160
Are you Chief Hu,

174
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,880
the highest commander
of the police station?

175
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,280
I need to tell you something.

176
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,240
Right now,

177
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,000
nothing is as important
as the explosion.

178
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,480
Let him in.

179
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,000
Aren't you Mr. Fang

180
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,360
who offended Mayor Gu's daughter?

181
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:12,760
You remember me.

182
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,360
May we have a word?

183
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:16,960
Okay.

184
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,880
You,

185
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:20,680
come here.

186
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,800
What's with the injuries on you?

187
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,160
You were caught in the explosion?

188
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,080
No, Chief Hu.

189
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,360
It's urgent.

190
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,560
I'll make a long story short.

191
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,880
I've come to ask for your help.

192
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,760
There are corrupt cops in your station.

193
